{"tid":1543791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8/9 星期日，甲組聯賽可以現場近距離欣賞警察踢波，同佢打打氣（免費）","createTime":"2019-09-05T10:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:58:04.000Z","uid":36494,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7e31b2db328060790fe4420341377ea3f8a94e9e","tid":1543791,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"8/9 星期日 <br />\n下午3:30分<br />\n甲組足球聯賽<br />\n九龍灣公園人造草場<br />\n黃大仙 vs 南華<br />\n免費入場<br />\n<br />\n今季南華邀請到前職業球員 現職警察的葉頌朗 加盟<br />\n<br />\n此球員2017年退出職業足球並投考警隊<br />\n現已貴為督察<br />\n<br />\n之前係社交媒體鬧爆示威者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oH8mSN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoH8mSN9.jpg&h=3fedfb8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港01亦有報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NxyJU5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NxyJU5.png&h=b191cf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位如果想親身近距離向勞苦功高的警察打打氣<br />\n到時請親身前往球場"},{"pid":"a9a6fb87ca0378a626878b2ad2ec16981bcf6729","tid":1543791,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:21:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/370798/%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83-%E5%8D%97%E8%8F%AF%E5%82%91%E5%BF%97%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3%E5%9C%98%E9%BD%8A%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2-%E8%AD%A6%E8%88%87%E6%B0%91%E7%82%BA%E6%95%B5-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E8%99%9F%E5%8F%AC910%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%2F370798%2F%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%2590%2583-%25E5%258D%2597%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%2582%2591%25E5%25BF%2597%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25BD%258A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2595%25B5-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%2599%259F%25E5%258F%25AC910%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%2585%258B&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MKi