(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9efde4c0c86218fa2f657a11f737feb37f3b62ba","tid":1543791,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:26:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f769fca2b56b3080048f8cc090ec6c79a1a77d0a","tid":1543791,"uid":14567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"啲波糧唔知佢申報左未呢"},{"pid":"5b2c10f1e5e7f439825ba2b3ed730c57f81cf634","tid":1543791,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:32:47.000Z","msg":"影衰南華"},{"pid":"bd79d7bd9a9a0991b24cfa22751464d8352df385","tid":1543791,"uid":28647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"一齊刺激球市"},{"pid":"573c71832c18bb707d3057b4bbfa1bdba85d5cd3","tid":1543791,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:36:02.000Z","msg":"有本地波球迷報料<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此警察會穿上 89 號南華波衫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家到時要集中為佢打氣"},{"pid":"1a3f8a01e32d3459b5a51f32b6309c7417a13f77","tid":1543791,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T10:46:16.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1368b1adfbb60c58a757bc1cd9a6d54f515f2711","tid":1543791,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-